# Patch notes for spacetimedb@2.6.1:
# - Upstream still serializes Result.err with variants[0]; use variants[1].
# - Upstream Prettify still maps primitives; preserve primitive types directly.
# - Upstream TableCache still compares object-backed range operands with raw
#   JavaScript ordering; normalize every supported native scalar first.
# - All three dispositions were re-verified against the published 2.6.1
#   tarball. Bun patches apply only to workspace installs; a published npm
#   consumer does not receive these fixes automatically.

